{"tid":1372002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【光復元朗】速龍小隊衝出西邊圍 數十白衣男持鐵通高呼：加油！","createTime":"2019-07-27T10:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T10:53:13.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"859849b11c7bef798c3afa8c286c219254e3bc90","tid":1372002,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T10:50:57.000Z","msg":"警方下午於元朗大馬路一帶與市民發生衝突，並施放多枚催淚彈驅趕，至下午5時許，近50名速龍小隊在西邊圍村內戒備，記者嘗試接近西邊圍村口時，遭村民趕離。與此同時，有數名手臂戴上紅色布章、手持鐵通的白衣村民在速龍小隊經過民居時「夾道歡迎」，站在路旁不斷高呼：「加油」鼓勵。 <br />\n<br />\n其後警方於西邊圍一度舉起橙旗，警告速離否則開槍，之後再度舉起黑旗。另外，有網民指多名手臂戴上紅色布章的西邊圍村民手持木棍在村內戒備，又在多間村屋內放置多枝鐵通。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190727/59870099\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190727%2F59870099&d=IcHW%2FfQ2zQNJFdNzTrXWKOgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=5a426f16\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190727%2F59870099&h=431b4730\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190727/59870099</a>"},{"pid":"28853b350d5dc7ca6a74622d23a866eccbf3f403","tid":1372002,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T10:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}